{"title":"Glowing dragon scale mail","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Glowing_dragon_scale_mail","type":"markdown","data":"| \\[   glowing dragon scale mail   |                                                     |\n| -------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |\n| Appearance                       | glowing dragon scale mail                           |\n|                                  |                                                     |\n| Slot                             | [body armor](/wiki/Body_armor \"Body armor\")         |\n| AC                               | [5](/wiki/Armor_class \"Armor class\")                |\n| Special                          | - [light source](/wiki/Light_source \"Light source\") |\n|                                  |                                                     |\n| Base price                       | 900 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                   |\n| Weight                           | [40](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                         |\n| Material                         | [dragon hide](/wiki/Dragon_hide \"Dragon hide\")      |\n\n| \\[   glowing dragon scales   |                                                     |\n| ---------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |\n| Appearance                   | glowing dragon scales                               |\n|                              |                                                     |\n| Slot                         | [body armor](/wiki/Body_armor \"Body armor\")         |\n| AC                           | [1](/wiki/Armor_class \"Armor class\")                |\n| Special                      | - [light source](/wiki/Light_source \"Light source\") |\n|                              |                                                     |\n| Base price                   | 500 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                   |\n| Weight                       | [40](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                         |\n| Material                     | [dragon hide](/wiki/Dragon_hide \"Dragon hide\")      |\n\n**Glowing dragon scale mail** is one of two new [dragon scale mails](/wiki/DSM \"DSM\") added in [UnNetHack](/wiki/UnNetHack \"UnNetHack\"). By default, glowing dragon scales and glowing dragon scale mail function as [light sources](/wiki/Light_source \"Light source\") [\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1).\n\nPrior to version 5.0.0, the glowing dragon's scales conferred [petrification resistance](/wiki/Petrification_resistance \"Petrification resistance\"). As of version 5.0.0, however, the breath types and resistances of all dragons (except the [chromatic dragon](/wiki/Chromatic_dragon_\\(UnNetHack\\) \"Chromatic dragon (UnNetHack)\")) are randomized, so the resistance conferred by glowing dragon scales depends on the breath type assigned to the glowing dragon.\n\nNote that in UnNetHack, dragon scale mail is considered a [magical item](/wiki/Magical_item \"Magical item\"), so it cannot be wished for, according to the [rules for wishing in UnNetHack](/wiki/Wish#UnNetHack \"Wish\"). Dragon scales, however, are acceptable. A note in the source code[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2) explains that this is because magic (a [scroll of enchant armor](/wiki/Scroll_of_enchant_armor \"Scroll of enchant armor\")) is required to produce the mail, but the scales are produced \"naturally\". Also, it is possible to wish for the scales that produce a specific resistance only if the appearance of that type is known, but it is possible to wish for scales from any dragon regardless of whether its resistance is known. Because \"glowing dragon\" is an appearance, glowing dragon scales can be wished for without knowing what resistance they give.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/do\\_wear.c in UnNetHack revision 1986, line 619](http://sourceforge.net/p/unnethack/code/1986/tree/trunk/src/do_wear.c#l619)\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/objects.c in UnNetHack revision 1986, line 334](http://sourceforge.net/p/unnethack/code/1986/tree/trunk/src/objects.c#l334)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Glowing dragon scale mail - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Glowing_dragon_scale_mail\",\"wgTitle\":\"Glowing dragon scale mail\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":95494,\"wgRevisionId\":95494,\"wgArticleId\":23567,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Dragon armor\",\"UnNetHack\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Glowing_dragon_scale_mail\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":23567,\"wgRequestId\":\"beac5a709202ef2bd628e976\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOptions\":\"{\\\"mode\\\":0,\\\"hideprefix\\\":20,\\\"showcount\\\":true,\\\"namespaces\\\":false}\"});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"user.options\":\"ready\",\"user.tokens\":\"loading\",\"ext.cite.styles\":\"r